					       <li outputclass="List 1" class="- topic/li ">
						         <p outputclass="List 1" class="- topic/p ">(a) Task/delivery orders issued in accordance with the terms of the basic contract except non-DoD orders ≥ $10M;</p>
					       </li>
					       <li outputclass="List 1" class="- topic/li ">
